[This is apparently the same outbreak reported earlier (see ProMED-mail
references cited above), but now seems to have spread to Kentucky. This is
not surprising since the Cincinnati metropolitan area extends across the
Ohio River into Kentucky, but microbiological characterization of strains
and the results of epidemiological investigations would still be of great
interest. - Mod.ES
